   <TEXT>
   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>HYMN NO.</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>61 8.5.8.5.D.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>Hosts of darkness are approaching</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>Satan leading on;</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>Lo, some fellow troops retreating,</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>Courage almost gone.</S>
   <S PAR='7' RSNT='1' SNO='7'>Chorus</S>
   <S PAR='8' RSNT='1' SNO='8'>Ho, be brave with faith unbending,</S>
   <S PAR='9' RSNT='1' SNO='9'>Standing patiently;</S>
   <S PAR='10' RSNT='1' SNO='10'>Soon by grace we'll shame the devil,</S>
   <S PAR='11' RSNT='1' SNO='11'>Gain the victory.</S>
   <S PAR='12' RSNT='1' SNO='12'>Lo, the blood-stained banner waving,</S>
   <S PAR='13' RSNT='1' SNO='13'>Hark, the trumpet sound;</S>
   <S PAR='14' RSNT='1' SNO='14'>In the pow'r of Christ we're standing,</S>
   <S PAR='15' RSNT='1' SNO='15'>Triumph will abound.</S>
   <S PAR='16' RSNT='1' SNO='16'>Jesus tells us, "I come quickly,</S>
   <S PAR='17' RSNT='1' SNO='17'>Stand, be watchful still."</S>
   <S PAR='18' RSNT='1' SNO='18'>We declare to highest heavens,</S>
   <S PAR='19' RSNT='1' SNO='19'>"By Your grace we will."</S>
   <S PAR='20' RSNT='1' SNO='20'>HYMN NO.</S>
   <S PAR='21' RSNT='1' SNO='21'>62 6.6.8.6.</S>
   <S PAR='22' RSNT='1' SNO='22'>God's people have been robbed,</S>
   <S PAR='23' RSNT='1' SNO='23'>And will not God avenge?</S>
   <S PAR='24' RSNT='1' SNO='24'>The Lord has said He surely will;</S>
   <S PAR='25' RSNT='1' SNO='25'>We needn't fear nor cringe.</S>
   <S PAR='26' RSNT='1' SNO='26'>We cry out night and day;</S>
   <S PAR='27' RSNT='1' SNO='27'>Will God not lend His ear?</S>
   <S PAR='28' RSNT='1' SNO='28'>Assuredly God's move is fast,</S>
   <S PAR='29' RSNT='1' SNO='29'>Vengeance from heaven's near.</S>
   <S PAR='30' RSNT='1' SNO='30'>When Satan presses hard,</S>
   <S PAR='31' RSNT='1' SNO='31'>Can God not reprehend?</S>
   <S PAR='32' RSNT='1' SNO='32'>Assuredly, God can and will,</S>
   <S PAR='33' RSNT='1' SNO='33'>And Satan's mischief end.</S>
   <S PAR='34' RSNT='1' SNO='34'>The enemy is fierce,</S>
   <S PAR='35' RSNT='1' SNO='35'>Our Lord has promised this.</S>
   <S PAR='36' RSNT='1' SNO='36'>We should cry out continually,</S>
   <S PAR='37' RSNT='1' SNO='37'>The termination his.</S>
   <S PAR='38' RSNT='1' SNO='38'>So we must not lose heart,</S>
   <S PAR='39' RSNT='1' SNO='39'>But ever stronger be.</S>
   <S PAR='40' RSNT='1' SNO='40'>Appeal to God both day and night;</S>
   <S PAR='41' RSNT='1' SNO='41'>Impair the enemy.</S>
   </TEXT>
  </BODY>
